                                        using  v                      .
       exe-acc-cmp-exi-920.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-acc-cmp-exi-999.
       exe-acc-cmp-exi-999.
           exit.

