      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento progressivo righe                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       00100                to   w-cix-ctr-prg          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento file righe [upr]                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
