      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-upr-000      thru wrt-rec-upr-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se modifica                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A trattamento modifica per testata      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-800.
       scr-mov-fil-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
