      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se inserimento                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-800.
           go to     scr-mov-fil-999.
       scr-mov-fil-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
