      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se at end : uscita                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to rew-rec-upr-999.
       rew-rec-upr-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
